{"type": "article", "id": 20751, "title": "屏风式衣柜", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-15T07:17:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110600H408OPpKSZ7GL1so.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个自带屏风功能的衣柜，打开两扇门后，还可以继续打开衣柜两侧的门，与衣柜后背构成一个平面。英国设计师 Nina Tolstrup 想要以此简化分割公共和私人空间的问题，无需安装墙面，只将衣柜放在卧室和客厅的中间，需要遮挡时打开它，很灵活。不过粉红色的衣柜实在太过少女，工业化生产之时最好多一些其他颜色。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110557Jgr9CxV5EzlnH6h4.gif\" width=\"468\" height=\"288\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61538462\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110558Z683nCjeKTQcGgiY.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110559BtouHVJsZ8rpKP6O.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"575\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61431624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110559U5mCoRx0MXHjweE2.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}